data.description: Discover perfection in this well-maintained 3-bed, 2.5-bath end unit townhouse. The open floor plan and high ceilings on the main level create a spacious atmosphere. The kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances, is a chef's delight. A main-level primary bedroom offers convenience with a full bathroom and walk-in closet. Upstairs, two bedrooms share a full bathroom. Don't miss the opportunity to tour this inviting home!
